Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:57.06,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Love will make my heart frail
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:02.52,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And so tender that I could crush it easily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:12.87,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never showed anyone any of my weaknesses till now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.04,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}I was able to endure any pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:25.00,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}But I didn't want to know this feeling
